snippet.title: Fury of Dracula: Digital Edition - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
#FuryofDracula #NomadGames #GamesWorkshop

Check out the official trailer for Fury of Dracula: Digital Edition! From the studio who bought you Talisman: Digital Edition comes another digital adaptation of a much loved Games Workshop board game. Will you stop Dracula, or become on of his bloody victims?

Add the game to your wishlist on Steam now! https://store.steampowered.com/app/958530/Fury_of_Dracula_Digital_Edition/
